race.comment: VELKA (5) lightly raced gelding who resumed with a fast finishing third over 1000m at Taree. Looks to have come back in good order and can go on with it here.  DIRTY DOES IT (8) tongue-tie goes on from the good gate and has a distinct fitness edge over the bulk of these. Closed late in a fast run contest when fourth over 1000m at this track. Well placed today and Luke Rolls keeps the ride. TOKE (13) even performance first-up from the lengthy break when fourth over 1000m at Muswellbrook. Finds an easier race with weight relief. Keep safe. INTELLIGENCER (11) warmed up late at her first run back with a solid fourth over 1000m at Taree. Winkers go on and can get off the mark this time in.
